item.title: Biratnagar Eye Hospital
item.description: (www.erec-p.org) Biratnagar Eye Hospital is a non-profitable, charitable eye hospital. It delivers affordable high quality eye care services to the economically poor and under-privileged people of the community. This hospital is an extension of Sagarmatha Choudhary Eye Hospital in Lahan started in September 2006.
